          "title": "ŒõiD Components",
          "content": "Every ŒõiD consists of five components: Lambda symbol (LUKHAS), tier designation, timestamp hash, symbolic character, and entropy hash."
        },
        {
          "title": "Tier System",
          "content": "ŒõiD uses a 6-tier system (0-5) providing progressively enhanced features and capabilities."
        },
        {
          "title": "Format Types",
          "content": "Standard format for individuals, commercial format for businesses, and enterprise format for organizations."
